            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">很好的普及读物，文笔稍微有些不足。</p>
        </div>
    </li>

                
    <li class="comment-item" data-cid="956886900">
        <div class="comment">
            <h3>
                <span class="comment-vote">
                    <span id="c-956886900" class="vote-count">0</span>
                        <a href="javascript:;" id="btn-956886900" class="j a_show_login" data-cid="956886900">有用</a>
                </span>
                <span class="comment-info">
                    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/kidsword/">子言</a>
                        <span class="user-stars allstar40 rating" title="推荐"></span>
                    <span>2015-09-06</span>
                </span>
            </h3>
            <p class="comment-content">文写的还不错，用典考据也很切实，但总有一种主观色彩太浓厚的感觉</p>
        </div>
    </li>

        </ul>
</div>

        

